and governments
don't necessarily take a part.

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:14.896
So in another case,
Anonymous vs. Los Zetas.

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:17.456
In early September 2011 in Mexico,

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:20.536
Los Zetas, one of the most
powerful drug cartels,

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:22.896
hung two bloggers with a sign that said,

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:26.600
"This is what will happen
to all Internet busybodies."

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:29.696
